    "name": "天道荒本纪 Chronicles of the Celestial Way",
    "steam_appid": 3185390,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方交流群：1215011858</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185390/extras/0d082ce4a79474a07f311a430be440b7.avif?t=1749208762\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185390/extras_big/0d082ce4a79474a07f311a430be440b7.avif?t=1749208762 width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>鸿蒙元年：起源</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鸿蒙初始，盘古诞生。他吸取了鸿蒙最多的元气，神力无穷，法力无边。然而他舍生取义，以自身衍化万物，使人界成为最大的自然界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185390/extras/25ab35c63fc36d38d27e40a2c41f592d.poster.avif?t=1749208762\" width=516 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185390/extras/25ab35c63fc36d38d27e40a2c41f592d.webm?t=1749208762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185390/extras/25ab35c63fc36d38d27e40a2c41f592d.mp4?t=1749208762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>鸿蒙百万年：古神孕育一</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经历百万年，鸿蒙元气再次爆发，孕育了第一批古神，而最厉害的，当属伏羲、女娲、东皇太一和天魔等寥寥数人 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>鸿蒙两百万年：古神孕育二</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鸿蒙元气最后一次爆发，第二批古神诞生了，这批古神所带的鸿蒙之气甚少，实力较弱，如夸父、刑天、黄鸟等等，只能依附于第一批的强大古神 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>鸿蒙两百二十万年：矛盾</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经历漫长的岁月，这些古神的内心发生了一些变化，尤其是天魔，他用吞噬空间的方式强化自己，成为了众矢之的，众神在域外星空决战天魔，战况十分惨烈，不少古神在这场战争中陨落了（妖界、鬼界等各界的起源），然而天魔的强大超出了众神的想象。最终，众神只能齐力将天魔封印在了域外星空 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185390/extras/c3b94aebcf51e138ffa3757185eb40c3.poster.avif?t=1749208762\" width=800 height=602 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185390/extras/c3b94aebcf51e138ffa3757185eb40c3.webm?t=1749208762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185390/extras/c3b94aebcf51e138ffa3757185eb40c3.mp4?t=1749208762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>洪荒历元年：纪年</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >众神来到了人界定居，各大部落形成，并开始了真正的纪年——洪荒历 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>洪荒历百年：战争持续</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战争并没有因此结束，信仰天魔的九黎族虎踞一方，各大部落也在明争暗斗，尤其金木水火土五大部落斗得最凶，人界并没有迎来真正的和平 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>洪荒历千年：千年之灾</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而才过千年，天魔的封印，松动了。天魔找到机会从封印的缝隙中透出大量魔气降临人间，九黎族的初代蚩尤吸收了大量的魔气，修为倍增，在蚩尤的统领下，九黎部落攻无不克，势如破竹。无奈之下五大部落之间只能发起联盟，共同对抗强大的蚩尤，却也仅仅抗住了九黎族的入侵，难分胜负 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>洪荒历1506年：女娲造人</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了对抗蚩尤，土之部落首领女娲提出了五德之体的计划，利用五行合一之力捏土造人，然而蚩尤并不会让他们计划得逞，再次向五大部落发动了战争</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185390/extras/db6432adcab4f7b77393340baa0a00e6.avif?t=1749208762\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185390/extras_big/db6432adcab4f7b77393340baa0a00e6.avif?t=1749208762 width=800 height=370 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
